### Get all active YouTube videos (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/youtube-videos/active
Content-Type: application/json

### Get all YouTube videos (Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/youtube-videos
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get a specific YouTube video by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/youtube-videos/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Create a new YouTube video (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/youtube-videos
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Church Video",
  "description": "A wonderful video about our church activities",
  "videoUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=example123",
  "thumbnailUrl": "https://img.youtube.com/vi/example123/maxresdefault.jpg",
  "displayOrder": 4,
  "active": true
}

### Update a YouTube video (Admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/youtube-videos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Video Title",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "videoUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=updated123",
  "thumbnailUrl": "https://img.youtube.com/vi/updated123/maxresdefault.jpg",
  "displayOrder": 1,
  "active": true
}

### Toggle active status (Admin only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/youtube-videos/1/toggle-active
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Delete a YouTube video (Admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/youtube-videos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
